msgid "Pācittiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on confession (<i lang=\"pi\">pācittiya</i>)"

#. </p><p> <span class="var" hidden>Bhojanavagga → dutiya­pavāra­ṇa­sikkhā­padaṃ (bj)</span>
